---
// Services Section - BLACK GYM
---

<section id="servicios" class="services section-padding">
  <div class="wide-container">
    <div class="section-header text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-4">
        NUESTROS <span class="text-green-500">SERVICIOS</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="section-line w-24 h-1 bg-green-500 mx-auto mb-8"></div>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Ofrecemos servicios especializados para garantizar tu éxito en el fitness
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="services-content grid md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <!-- Instalación de Equipos -->
      <div class="service-item group text-center p-8 bg-gray-900 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-green-500 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
        <div class="service-icon mb-6">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-green-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-black text-3xl font-bold group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <i class="fas fa-tools"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4 group-hover:text-green-500 transition-colors">
          Instalación de Equipos
        </h3>
        
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Servicio completo de instalación y configuración de equipos en tu gimnasio o hogar.
        </p>
        
        <div class="service-features space-y-2 text-sm">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 text-gray-300">
            <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 text-xs"></i>
            <span>Instalación profesional</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 text-gray-300">
            <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 text-xs"></i>
            <span>Configuración completa</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 text-gray-300">
            <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 text-xs"></i>
            <span>Pruebas de funcionamiento</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="service-action mt-6">
          <a 
            href="https://wa.me/50250509724?text=Hola%2C%20necesito%20servicio%20de%20instalación%20de%20equipos" 
            target="_blank" 
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 text-green-500 hover:text-green-400 font-medium transition-colors"
          >
            <span>Solicitar servicio</span>
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-right text-sm"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Asesoría Personalizada -->
      <div class="service-item group text-center p-8 bg-gray-900 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-green-500 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
        <div class="service-icon mb-6">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-green-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-black text-3xl font-bold group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <i class="fas fa-user-tie"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4 group-hover:text-green-500 transition-colors">
          Asesoría Personalizada
        </h3>
        
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Te ayudamos a elegir los equipos y suplementos perfectos para tus objetivos.
        </p>
        
        <div class="service-features space-y-2 text-sm">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 text-gray-300">
            <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 text-xs"></i>
            <span>Consulta personalizada</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 text-gray-300">
            <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 text-xs"></i>
            <span>Análisis de necesidades</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 text-gray-300">
            <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 text-xs"></i>
            <span>Recomendaciones expertas</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="service-action mt-6">
          <a 
            href="https://wa.me/50250509724?text=Hola%2C%20necesito%20asesoría%20personalizada%20para%20equipos%20y%20suplementos" 
            target="_blank" 
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 text-green-500 hover:text-green-400 font-medium transition-colors"
          >
            <span>Solicitar asesoría</span>
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-right text-sm"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Entrega a Domicilio -->
      <div class="service-item group text-center p-8 bg-gray-900 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-green-500 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
        <div class="service-icon mb-6">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-green-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-black text-3xl font-bold group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <i class="fas fa-shipping-fast"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4 group-hover:text-green-500 transition-colors">
          Entrega a Domicilio
        </h3>
        
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Servicio de entrega en toda la región de Chimaltenango y áreas cercanas.
        </p>
        
        <div class="service-features space-y-2 text-sm">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 text-gray-300">
            <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 text-xs"></i>
            <span>Entrega rápida</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 text-gray-300">
            <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 text-xs"></i>
            <span>Cobertura regional</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 text-gray-300">
            <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 text-xs"></i>
            <span>Productos protegidos</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="service-action mt-6">
          <a 
            href="https://wa.me/50250509724?text=Hola%2C%20consulto%20sobre%20entrega%20a%20domicilio" 
            target="_blank" 
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 text-green-500 hover:text-green-400 font-medium transition-colors"
          >
            <span>Consultar entrega</span>
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-right text-sm"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Mantenimiento -->
      <div class="service-item group text-center p-8 bg-gray-900 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-green-500 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
        <div class="service-icon mb-6">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-green-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-black text-3xl font-bold group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <i class="fas fa-wrench"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4 group-hover:text-green-500 transition-colors">
          Mantenimiento
        </h3>
        
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Servicio técnico especializado para mantener tus equipos en óptimas condiciones.
        </p>
        
        <div class="service-features space-y-2 text-sm">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 text-gray-300">
            <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 text-xs"></i>
            <span>Revisión preventiva</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 text-gray-300">
            <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 text-xs"></i>
            <span>Reparaciones expertas</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 text-gray-300">
            <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 text-xs"></i>
            <span>Repuestos originales</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="service-action mt-6">
          <a 
            href="https://wa.me/50250509724?text=Hola%2C%20necesito%20servicio%20de%20mantenimiento%20para%20mis%20equipos" 
            target="_blank" 
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 text-green-500 hover:text-green-400 font-medium transition-colors"
          >
            <span>Solicitar mantenimiento</span>
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-right text-sm"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Additional Service Info -->
    <div class="service-guarantee mt-16 text-center">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900 to-gray-800 rounded-lg p-8 border border-gray-700">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
          <i class="fas fa-shield-alt text-green-500 mr-2"></i>
          Garantía de Calidad
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Todos nuestros servicios están respaldados por nuestra garantía de satisfacción. 
          Trabajamos con técnicos certificados y utilizamos repuestos originales para 
          asegurar la máxima calidad en cada servicio.
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-8">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-3">
            <i class="fas fa-medal text-green-500 text-xl"></i>
            <span class="text-white font-medium">Técnicos Certificados</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-3">
            <i class="fas fa-clock text-green-500 text-xl"></i>
            <span class="text-white font-medium">Servicio Rápido</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-3">
            <i class="fas fa-handshake text-green-500 text-xl"></i>
            <span class="text-white font-medium">Garantía Total</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .services {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000000 0%, #1a1a1a 100%);
  }
  
  .wide-container {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }
  
  .section-padding {
    padding: 80px 0;
  }
  
  .service-item:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.1);
  }
  
  .service-icon::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
    border-radius: 50%;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .service-item:hover .service-icon::after {
    opacity: 1;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .services-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .section-padding {
      padding: 60px 0;
    }
  }
</style>
